There are six main types of comparisons:

\describe{
\item{REPRODUCIBILITY}{Same pipeline (\code{same_bioinfo_pipeline = TRUE}),
same primer/technology (\code{same_primer_seq_tech = TRUE}), same samples.
Used to test \strong{reproducibility} of results when running the exact same
